spanGrp.span: But the woman did not sing.
Men and women went to work together.
amatote mol- phe- mol valova no
This is taken from the hill- vall- hillside.
phebu̠ molbu̠ vacha mol chabung abung- bungnu̠
Valley rice... hill rice... rice crops, threshed...
Valley rice, while threshing valley rice
mol valote so va phe valote so va
Taken from the hillside and taken from valleys.
Vahrangna tuna (to ne) ātu- ātupeval (hin ning) ama java
Amate vahrang tuna te tungnung maja varende
